dct_title_s: United States, featuring the interstate highway system / General Drafting Company ; [prepared for] Humble Oil & Refining Co. (Verso)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Panel title. On recto: map covers west United States. Ancillary maps: Alaska and Hawaii. Includes on recto: mileage chart. On verso: map continued at different scale covering east United States. Ancillary map Florida continued."How to estimate distances"
dct_publisher_sm: Convent Station, N.J. : General Drafting Company, 1966.
